10.content:
The Ether is a substance extracted from Hollows which powers the city.
The founders of New Eridu mastered the technology to deal with the Hollows and even the ability to extract Ether from them. Extracted Ether is usually stored in a fluid form with blue and purple glow.
The substance is corruptive if not handled and contained properly.
 Ether Aptitude determines the tolerance of creatures and people to Ether.
Ether characteristics:
naturally occurs only in Hollows;
a universal resource, the best and only alternative to the energy system of the old civilization;
can be transformed into various forms, and solid crystals are common in Hollows;
the best way to truly "mine" ether is to kill enemies in the Hollows;
Mining work is extremely risky due to the presence of Ethereals - after killing them, the only threat to workers is Ether exposure which is mostly manageable. 
Ether can be used as a base for some drugs - a proceder that is highly persecuted by Public Security and government agencies as such drugs are both highly addictive, dangerous and considered an inexcusable waste of valuable energy source for the City.

